                            <comment id="12763654" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 8 Oct 2009 19:40:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this patch incorporates Brandon&apos;s test and replaces the undocumented CF attribute aliases with a single human-readable &quot;comment&quot; attribute.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
